</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="138" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,150,861]" pageId="5" pageNumber="138">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,799,825]" pageId="5" pageNumber="138">Etymology.</emphasis>
The new species is named for Nadezhda Yavorskaya, a Russian chironomidologist, who actively collects stoneflies, including this interesting species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
